spud (1.1.1) natty; urgency=low

  * Offer two major new features in Diamond: slice view and group view.
  * Slicing shows all instances of a particular entry, along with its
    data and attributes.
  * Grouping modifies the treeview to only show all instances of a
    particular entry.

 -- Patrick Farrell <patrick.farrell06@imperial.ac.uk>  Tue, 26 Jul 2011 17:37:17 +0100

